#: ../../../topics/benchmarking.rst:5
msgid "Benchmarking"
msgstr "基準測試"

#: ../../../topics/benchmarking.rst:9
msgid ""
"Scrapy comes with a simple benchmarking suite that spawns a local HTTP "
"server and crawls it at the maximum possible speed. The goal of this "
"benchmarking is to get an idea of how Scrapy performs in your hardware, in "
"order to have a common baseline for comparisons. It uses a simple spider "
"that does nothing and just follows links."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/benchmarking.rst:15
msgid "To run it use::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/benchmarking.rst:17
msgid "scrapy bench"
msgstr ""

